{"tid":1398320,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"睇住呢種柒真係令人心頭一振","createTime":"2019-08-02T18:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T03:56:21.000Z","uid":216021,"like":15,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"329d21ce67ca5714e893ad84b20755c53b637f2e","tid":1398320,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:17:46.000Z","msg":"睇住呢種柒真係令人心頭一振<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n季初係咁燈，搞到響公海比人笑，已經柒一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n季中連横再燈，燈到又入波又助攻，又柒一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果迫住唔屌又屌 燈到隻75m荷蘭狗贏埋英超mvp，柒第三獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見雲狗早兩個月 燈到天昏地暗，以為咩偉論君臨咁巴閉啦，屌你老母一睇，嘩，燈撚到吖，我睇緊利歐聯捧杯啊75m 鐵衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩條友可以由上至下都柒到咁勻循、咁立體、咁不堪入目，仲要自以為串到利物浦，世上真係得雲迪克愛助攻做得到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c530f6377173d0e25b8e464fbc04b73769816675","tid":1398320,"uid":135461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"佢係咪死能左"},{"pid":"aeaa5d4b3f452898f15bea323358ef2cc1229e6b","tid":1398320,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df69a2ffbd5b5168231b2db7eee4edfdc6bbdc16","tid":1398320,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeaa5d4b3f452898f15bea323358ef2cc1229e6b","tid":1398320,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:27:02.000Z","msg":"羅蛇含撚LA"},{"pid":"16e3def566c621f51290a115199f0b791ece5731","tid":1398320,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df69a2ffbd5b5168231b2db7eee4edfdc6bbdc16","tid":1398320,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeaa5d4b3f452898f15bea323358ef2cc1229e6b","tid":1398320,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:27:02.000Z","msg":"羅蛇含撚LA"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:27:34.000Z","msg":"又jer"}